These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, collecting
City: liverpool, prague
1. the person traveling to liverpool is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to prague is the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | collecting | card-games |
| City     | prague    | liverpool   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: zucchini, cherry
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: sailing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is sailing is in an odd position##4
2. the person eating cherry is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Food   | cherry | zucchini        |
| Sport      | sailing  | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, house
House: palace, farmhouse
1. the palace house is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of ambient##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | house    | ambient |
| House   | palace | farmhouse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade
2 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog
1. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | 7up      | lemonade |
| Pet       | mouse | hedgehog    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
