 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, june
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Birthday       | june | january  |
| Transport   | ship  | motorbike |

 #################################

 
