.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
2 different games are played: scrabble, domino
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: skiing, volleyball
1. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Game   | domino | scrabble   |
| Sport         | skiing | volleyball |

 #################################

 
